                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/images/hotel3.jpg" alt="Microsoft Azure" class="img-responsive" />
            <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                <p>
                    Our spacious rooms are large enough to host a stampede of cockroaches!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/images/hotel4.jpg" alt="Microsoft Azure" class="img-responsive" />
            <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                <p>
                    The sofas smell like new.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/images/hotel5.jpg" alt="Microsoft Azure" class="img-responsive" />
            <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                <p>
                    Our light bulbs are the brightest.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/images/hotel6.jpg" alt="Microsoft Azure" class="img-responsive" />
            <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                <p>
                    Spend money at the restaurant.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
</div>
